<%# app/views/pages/top.html.erb %>
<section class="py-8 sm:py-12">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-teal-700">
      ワクワクできる迷路を作ろう！解こう！みんなでシェアしよう！
    </p>
    <h2 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl">
      ♻️ Make Mazes! 🐏
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-8 text-slate-600 sm:text-lg">
      「入口から出口まで。」<br />あなたが想うように描く一本の線から、 オリジナル迷路を作れるアプリです。</p>
    <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-8 text-slate-600 sm:text-lg">
      <b>だれでも迷路を「作って」「解いて」「共有」して楽しめます</b>🧩</p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
      <%= link_to "迷路をつくる！", new_maze_path,
          class: "inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-teal-700 sm:w-auto" %>

      <%= link_to "使いかたガイド", "#",
          class: "inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-50 sm:w-auto" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
